{
  "texts": [
    "This work aims to fill that gap.",
    "MethodologyIn this study, we conducted experiments to assess the efficacy of an encoder-only model in contrast to a decoder-only model, specifically in the domains of intent classification and sentiment analysis.",
    "Both models underwent fine-tuning using curated benchmark datasets comprising text utterances annotated with intent labels and sentiment labels.",
    "Furthermore, the decoder-only model underwent evaluation utilizing few-shot learning methodologies.",
    "Additionally, an in-depth analysis of operational outcomes, including output latency, was undertaken."
  ]
}